snippet.title: Batman: Arkham City - Game of the Year Edition
snippet.description:
Find us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/batmanarkhamcity

Batman: Arkham City The Game of the Year Edition includes:

o Full Game with all Updates
o All new DLC (Harley Quinn's Revenge)
o All previously released DLC packs
o Movie Download: Batman Year One (USA and Canada only)
